## Decisions and Action Items
* **Liaison Management Drafts**: The drafts `draft-iab-liaison-mgt-rfc4052bis` and `draft-iab-liaison-mgt-rfc4053bis` will be reviewed by the IAB for approval, then submitted to the IESG to begin the AD-sponsored IETF last call process.
* **Protocol Greasing**: The authors of `draft-iab-protocol-greasing` will incorporate feedback regarding ECH greasing, add cautionary notes on over-allocating grease space to prevent protocol exhaustion, and evaluate other specialized greasing examples (e.g., `draft-ietf-dnsop-grease`).